summary:
A young female Dak Elf preset for RaceMenu (You can use this preset for other races)
Obviously, her name is referring to the Egyptian Goddess, nothing else...
descriptionHtml:
Hello,
This is a preset of Isis, a young Dark Elf female. But you can use this preset for other races.
This is one of my rare contribution for the Skyrim Nexus.
I hope you like her!

[b]Step 1 - Requirements :[/b]
[url=http://skse.silverlock.org/]SKSE
[/url][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/24273/?]Etheral Elven Overhaul[/url] by Nuska
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/24273/?]RaceMenu v3 or more [color=#ffffff]by Expired[/color]

[/url]Step 2 - Mods recommended :

Body and face texture : [b][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/35267/?]SG Female Textures Renewal[/url] (by Hello Santa)[/b]

Hair : [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/10168/?]ApachiiSkyHair[/url] by Apachii
Eyes : [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/13722/]The Eyes Of Beauty[/url] by Gabriel Mailhot
Lips : [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/22701/?]Seductive Lips HD[/url]  by [b]EcthelionOtW[/b]
Make up : [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/31665/?]Better Makeup for SKSE[/url] by [b]Diethardt[/b]
ENB preset : I use [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/67441/?]Dovah Nakiin[/url] by Machok in my screenshoots. Other ENB are nice too.

Step 3 - How to install

Copy the file DarkElf_Isis2.jslot here : Skyrim\Data\SKSE\Plugins\CharGen\Presets
Go into showracemenu
Go on the preset tab
Hit F9 for load the preset. 
Choose the preset DarkElf_Isis2.jslot

I you like this preset, take a look at my other presets and my [url=https://www.flickr.com/photos/132183542@N06/]Flickr gallery[/url]

Enjoy!
author: Poupoulou
